title: Carrot and cranberry muffins
ingredients: ['125g plain flour', '120g wholemeal flour', '1 tablespoon chia seeds', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/4 teaspoon ground ginger', '120g unsalted butter, room temperature', '100g soft brown sugar, or to taste', '50g caster sugar, or to taste', '1 egg', '1 banana', '225g grated carrots', '1 tablespoon grated orange zest', '75g dried cranberries, or more to taste']
